long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Visual update to 112's website. Easier to find commonly used files and key dates. Applies one of 3 themes to every page to optimize your browsing experience.

༼ つ ◕_◕ ༽つ  

*** 3 new themes to choose from (Light, Dark, and Night)
*** Works on every page
*** Click to copy PWD
*** Quick Navigation links (Home, Syllabus, Assignments, Old Exams, Lecture Notes, Languages, Checklist, and Pair Programming)
***Highlight key dates
***Pretty Calendar
